1
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:08,540
=Fireworks=

2
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:10,860
=Episode 4=

3
00:00:16,879 --> 00:00:18,160
(So they were waiting for me?)

4
00:00:19,079 --> 00:00:20,120
(Fine, let's get it done.)

5
00:00:28,199 --> 00:00:29,239
(What's going on?)

6
00:00:29,500 --> 00:00:31,580
(Where are the promised
prediction and counterattack features?)

7
00:00:32,880 --> 00:00:34,000
Sorry.

8
00:00:34,119 --> 00:00:35,520
I forgot to turn on defense mode.

9
00:00:35,920 --> 00:00:37,640
Hey,

10
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:38,359
hurry up!

11
00:00:38,359 --> 00:00:40,310
If you don't move faster,
I'm going to get killed!

12
00:00:40,320 --> 00:00:41,280
Wait,

13
00:00:41,280 --> 00:00:42,520
it's almost ready.

14
00:00:54,020 --> 00:00:55,580
(Wing Chun)

15
00:01:10,319 --> 00:01:13,400
Qiao Nian, did my moves
just now look cool?

16
00:01:13,439 --> 00:01:15,359
This guy's talking to himself.

17
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:16,599
Is he crazy?

18
00:01:17,319 --> 00:01:18,120
Qiao Nian...

19
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:36,480
Cool.

20
00:01:37,879 --> 00:01:38,840
Really cool.

21
00:01:43,100 --> 00:01:45,120
(Consciousness Space)

22
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:45,920
Qiao Nian!

23
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,079
Qiao Nian,

24
00:01:48,879 --> 00:01:50,040
why were you so stupid?

25
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:54,439
Why did you take that knife for me?

26
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,079
Zechen...

27
00:01:57,439 --> 00:02:01,239
Lucky I saved you.

28
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:05,040
Was I awesome or what?

29
00:02:08,100 --> 00:02:15,620
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

30
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,599
Zechen,

31
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:22,199
I can't feel anything anymore.

32
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:26,560
I think I'm running out of time.

33
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:29,039
No, that's not true.

34
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:32,120
It's not time yet.

35
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:33,730
We said it would be seven days.

36
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,479
Zechen...

37
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,639
I don't want to die.

38
00:02:42,620 --> 00:02:46,020
♪Yet I still want you close♪

39
00:02:46,020 --> 00:02:49,940
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

40
00:02:50,300 --> 00:02:53,340
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

41
00:02:54,599 --> 00:02:55,439
Qiao Nian!

42
00:02:56,439 --> 00:02:57,360
Qiao Nian!

43
00:02:59,280 --> 00:02:59,800
Qiao Nian!

44
00:03:00,919 --> 00:03:01,439
Qiao Nian!

45
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,759
Qiao Nian!

46
00:03:28,340 --> 00:03:30,900
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

47
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,319
Qiao Nian...

48
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:36,400
Jiang Zechen, you're awake.

49
00:03:39,199 --> 00:03:40,000
Wen Li,

50
00:03:40,639 --> 00:03:42,719
check the hospital surveillance.

51
00:03:43,319 --> 00:03:45,319
Find out where things went wrong.

52
00:03:45,319 --> 00:03:46,120
Okay.

53
00:03:47,650 --> 00:03:48,680
What are you going to do?

54
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,280
I'm going to see Grandpa.

55
00:03:53,479 --> 00:03:54,800
Be careful with your wound!

56
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,159
Move!

57
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,400
I need to see Grandpa!

58
00:04:03,039 --> 00:04:05,639
Mr. Jiang, Mr. Qiao is unwell.

59
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,800
He can't see you right now.

60
00:04:06,919 --> 00:04:09,599
Don't think I don't know
what Qiao Wenjun is doing.

61
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:12,240
You'll pay for this too.

62
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:17,879
Hey! I have something
important to tell Grandpa!

63
00:04:20,940 --> 00:04:22,860
(Grandpa)

64
00:04:31,399 --> 00:04:32,199
Wenjun!

65
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:35,399
Release Qiao Nian right now!

66
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:37,920
Jiang Zechen?

67
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:44,759
You're no match for me.

68
00:04:45,439 --> 00:04:47,800
The number you have
dialed is currently unavailable.

69
00:04:48,319 --> 00:04:49,040
Wenjun!

70
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,399
Go!

71
00:04:51,319 --> 00:04:52,120
Wenjun!

72
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:54,920
(I lost Qiao Nian.)

73
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:57,800
(I can't find Grandpa either.)

74
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,560
Zechen!

75
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,879
I'm here, Zechen!

76
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,360
(Qiao Nian...)

77
00:05:13,759 --> 00:05:15,000
(This is all my fault.)

78
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,879
(I'm sorry.)

79
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,920
Qiao Nian, I'm back.

80
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:34,639
Zechen, have some grapes.

81
00:05:35,319 --> 00:05:36,120
(Qiao Nian...)

82
00:05:37,759 --> 00:05:40,079
(Are you really gone?)

83
00:05:40,639 --> 00:05:41,800
Let's get a divorce.

84
00:05:44,580 --> 00:05:49,860
(Divorce Agreement)

85
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,120
(No matter the reason,)

86
00:05:55,439 --> 00:05:57,079
(I shouldn't have kept things from you.)

87
00:05:57,680 --> 00:06:01,160
Jiang Zechen, if you want
to see your brother again,

88
00:06:01,279 --> 00:06:04,199
you have to earn
Qiao Qibang's granddaughter's trust.

89
00:06:04,399 --> 00:06:08,000
Qiao Nian is your classmate, right?

90
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:10,319
Get out of the Qiao family right now!

91
00:06:10,319 --> 00:06:11,319
Duan Yiran, don't touch me!

92
00:06:11,319 --> 00:06:12,399
What if I do?

93
00:06:12,399 --> 00:06:13,150
What are you doing?

94
00:06:14,879 --> 00:06:16,000
Trash stays trash.

95
00:06:16,319 --> 00:06:17,519
You'll never belong here.

96
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,519
At least I'm a Qiao.

97
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,040
I'm part of this family.

98
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,959
Who do you think you are,

99
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,480
acting all high and mighty?

100
00:06:29,079 --> 00:06:29,879
Hey!

101
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:31,199
Let Qiao Nian go!

102
00:06:32,519 --> 00:06:33,600
Qiao Nian, let's go!

103
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:39,040
Thanks, Jiang Zechen.

104
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:45,040
I made this myself.

105
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:46,839
It's for you.

106
00:06:47,839 --> 00:06:49,360
Wow, it's beautiful.

107
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,480
There's a button on it.

108
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:55,079
Press it and it activates a tracker.

109
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:57,079
If you're ever in danger,

110
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:59,199
I'll find you right away.

111
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:01,519
I'm sorry.

112
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,959
I'm so sorry, Qiao Nian.

113
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,879
I didn't protect you.

114
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:12,959
Qiao Nian!

115
00:07:14,839 --> 00:07:16,199
Qiao Nian!

116
00:07:16,199 --> 00:07:19,500
♪I have waited for sunsets
where mountains and seas glow♪

117
00:07:19,980 --> 00:07:23,300
♪I have waited for the moon
to wander and stars to shift and flow♪

118
00:07:23,660 --> 00:07:29,300
♪Yet I never waited for nights
with you and a painted world♪

119
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,759
(I let you down.)

120
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:32,680
(I let Grandpa down.)

121
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:37,480
(I need to find Grandpa for Qiao Nian.)

122
00:07:44,860 --> 00:07:47,980
(Jiang Zechen)

123
00:07:54,980 --> 00:07:56,140
(Grandpa)

124
00:07:59,199 --> 00:08:00,000
Wenjun,

125
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,279
let go of me right now.

126
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:04,680
Stop this.

127
00:08:10,959 --> 00:08:12,560
Your grandson-in-law is

128
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,040
really getting on my nerves.

129
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:16,940
(Sorry, the number you dialed
is turned off.)

130
00:08:17,279 --> 00:08:18,079
Grandpa...

131
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:21,199
(Grandpa's in danger!)

132
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:23,759
Wenjun,

133
00:08:24,879 --> 00:08:27,879
do you remember what I told you when you

134
00:08:29,279 --> 00:08:31,079
first joined the company?

135
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,879
Making mistakes isn't the issue.

136
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:36,840
What matters is what you do after.

137
00:08:38,279 --> 00:08:41,799
I remember every word you said.

138
00:08:42,759 --> 00:08:44,399
Since you remember,

139
00:08:45,679 --> 00:08:47,919
then release Qiao Nian right now.

140
00:08:48,279 --> 00:08:49,080
Dad,

141
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,679
what are you saying?

142
00:08:53,159 --> 00:08:54,279
Even now,

143
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:56,840
you're still thinking about Qiao Nian?

144
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,399
Wenjun,

145
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:05,240
bring Qiao Nian back right now.

146
00:09:06,519 --> 00:09:09,840
I'll pretend

147
00:09:10,799 --> 00:09:12,679
nothing happened.

148
00:09:14,759 --> 00:09:16,480
How did you know it was me?

149
00:09:16,919 --> 00:09:18,799
No one knows you better than me.

150
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:20,720
Wenjun,

151
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:23,840
I know your ability,

152
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:27,399
and I know your loyalty.

153
00:09:28,879 --> 00:09:29,679
But...

154
00:09:30,919 --> 00:09:34,240
You've used it the wrong way.

155
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:35,039
Dad,

156
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:38,120
I won't even talk
about how you always favored Zhenxuan.

157
00:09:38,679 --> 00:09:39,919
But why are you

158
00:09:39,919 --> 00:09:42,080
siding with Qiao Nian?

159
00:09:43,559 --> 00:09:46,120
I've spent most
of my life for this company.

160
00:09:47,279 --> 00:09:49,000
Zhenxuan refused the arranged marriage,

161
00:09:49,159 --> 00:09:50,159
I did it.

162
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,840
When he refused to run the company,

163
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:53,799
I stepped in.

164
00:09:53,799 --> 00:09:55,919
When he refused to come home,

165
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:59,639
I was always by your side.

166
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:08,879
You say I used my abilities wrong,

167
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,799
but your "right way"

168
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:17,399
nearly ruined the company.

169
00:10:18,519 --> 00:10:19,480
It was me!

170
00:10:20,879 --> 00:10:24,639
I saved it!

171
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:25,879
Wenjun,

172
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,399
good job.

173
00:10:28,399 --> 00:10:29,639
This project will

174
00:10:29,639 --> 00:10:33,120
save Qiao Group.

175
00:10:34,799 --> 00:10:35,600
Zhenxuan,

176
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:39,440
you'll take over it.

177
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,080
Dad...

178
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:41,000
Dad,

179
00:10:41,759 --> 00:10:43,039
this is my project.

180
00:10:43,679 --> 00:10:46,240
It's now your brother's.

181
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:47,960
Why?

182
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,360
Why?

183
00:10:50,879 --> 00:10:52,120
Why?

184
00:10:54,159 --> 00:10:56,440
I used to think you just favored sons

185
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:58,279
over daughters, so I endured it.

186
00:10:58,879 --> 00:11:01,840
But now you're even favoring Qiao Nian?

187
00:11:05,559 --> 00:11:09,320
So you really don't love me at all.

188
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:11,240
Wenjun,

189
00:11:13,159 --> 00:11:15,799
I'm grateful for everything you've done.

190
00:11:16,879 --> 00:11:19,159
But we both know how you

191
00:11:19,159 --> 00:11:21,039
saved the company!

192
00:11:21,519 --> 00:11:25,399
That method brings too many risks!

193
00:11:25,759 --> 00:11:29,960
You might even get trapped yourself!

194
00:11:30,279 --> 00:11:32,159
Hmph.

195
00:11:33,679 --> 00:11:35,080
So what?

196
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:37,919
As long as the result is good,

197
00:11:38,919 --> 00:11:40,360
why care about the process?

198
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:44,639
If you care so much about Qiao Nian,

199
00:11:46,519 --> 00:11:49,279
then trade the entire Qiao Group for her.

200
00:11:53,639 --> 00:11:54,440
Wenjun...

201
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:56,879
Medicine...

202
00:11:58,120 --> 00:11:58,919
Medicine...

203
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:02,279
Medicine...

204
00:12:04,879 --> 00:12:06,720
Where are the share transfer papers?

205
00:12:08,879 --> 00:12:09,679
Medicine...

206
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:11,399
Tell me.

207
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:14,120
Where are the share transfer papers?

208
00:12:14,919 --> 00:12:17,159
Medicine...

209
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:21,759
Wenjun, I'm not telling you a thing.

210
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:24,759
Wenjun...

211
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:30,519
Medicine...

212
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,639
Medicine...

213
00:12:35,879 --> 00:12:37,200
Medicine...

214
00:12:40,440 --> 00:12:41,679
Wenjun...

215
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:45,480
Wen...

216
00:12:50,800 --> 00:12:56,770
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

217
00:12:57,050 --> 00:13:04,650
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

218
00:13:04,700 --> 00:13:08,490
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

219
00:13:09,010 --> 00:13:12,290
♪Where this ends♪

220
00:13:12,290 --> 00:13:19,570
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

221
00:13:19,570 --> 00:13:23,900
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

222
00:13:23,940 --> 00:13:27,020
♪Love turns into pain♪

223
00:13:27,090 --> 00:13:31,210
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

224
00:13:31,370 --> 00:13:34,850
♪Yet I still want you close♪

225
00:13:34,850 --> 00:13:39,020
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

226
00:13:39,020 --> 00:13:42,330
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

227
00:13:42,330 --> 00:13:46,900
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

228
00:13:46,900 --> 00:13:53,210
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

229
00:13:53,800 --> 00:13:57,990
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

230
00:13:57,990 --> 00:14:01,210
♪Love turns into pain♪

231
00:14:01,210 --> 00:14:05,650
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

232
00:14:05,650 --> 00:14:09,000
♪Yet I still want you close♪

233
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:13,230
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

234
00:14:13,270 --> 00:14:16,490
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

235
00:14:16,620 --> 00:14:21,210
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

236
00:14:21,210 --> 00:14:28,290
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪
